OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fovernight, with largely clear skies
OL,7,Fand just the small risk of some
OL,8,Fshallow mist and fog. Winds generally
OL,9,Feasing across the region and turning
OL,10,Fchilly, with a frost possible in
OL,11,Fsheltered rural spots.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FAny patchy fog will clear
OL,14,Fquickly to give a fine day with plenty
OL,15,Fof sunshine. Generally mild but
OL,16,Ffeeling cooler, particularly towards
OL,17,Fthe east coast, with a fresh easterly
OL,18,Fbreeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
